@startuml
title Figure 5.10: Update Pricing Sequence Diagram

actor "System Administrator" as Maintainer
participant "prices.json" as PriceFile
participant "Configuration Loader\n(src/config.js)" as Config
participant "Pricing Service\n(src/pricing.js)" as Pricing
participant "Application Runtime" as Runtime

Maintainer -> PriceFile : Edit product catalog values
Maintainer -> Runtime : Restart application
Runtime -> Config : load prices.json
Config -> PriceFile : read file
PriceFile --> Config : catalog data
Config --> Runtime : exported prices object
Runtime -> Pricing : use updated catalog for quotes

note right of Maintainer
TODO: The current implementation supports file-based
price maintenance only. No runtime dashboard API exists.
end note

@enduml
